🛡️ Cool Defence – Client Website
Developed for Digambara Industries
📌 Overview
Cool Defence is a professional business website developed for Digambara Industries, a manufacturer of Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) based in Pune, India.
The website is designed to present the company's products, certifications, and services in a clean, modern, and user-friendly manner. It focuses on delivering a strong digital presence for industrial clients and improving customer engagement.

🏭 About the Client
Digambara Industries is a DEF manufacturer established in 2006, specializing in ISO 22241 compliant products for modern diesel engines. The company serves industrial clients, fleet operators, and distributors with reliable and high-quality solutions.

